parameters:
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Mother, I will definitely become a direct-line mage... just like
you...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lady Lucia, you were here after all. What's the matter?

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Hehe... It's the same as always. Mother won't pass on the direct-line
power to me.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] How about you? Do you think you can master the Blue Magic?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yes. The training is tough, but somehow I will manage to learn it.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] I see. That's good to hear.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Luna, I want to go to the lower world again.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] The lower world wasn't peaceful, but there were countries like the
Kingdom of Lyubel and the Free Country of Moduna that shared our
values.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I don't know about the eternally neutral Moduna, but Lyubel was a
country that had renounced war. Prince Reenu and Lady Lucia would make
a perfect couple~.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] But Prince Reenu might be a bit my type~.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Hehe, but too bad, I have Mido after all.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Hehe... So Lady Lucia really likes Mido-san.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Yes. Luna, let's eat together once you bring the lunch.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Now, what shall we eat first~?
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] What is it~? We're close, aren't we~? Don't be shy.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Can I call you... big sister?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I've been so happy since Lady Lucia picked me up. You've treated me
just like a real sister, so I just... I'm sorry for saying something
weird.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Luna, call me 'big sister'. I wasn't wrong in choosing you as a court
magician.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Ahaha... It feels a bit embarrassing.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I'll call you 'big sister' when I feel like it~.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Ahaha, what's with that~? Saying it on your own~.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Let's eat our lunch quickly. It's going to get cold.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lady Lucia, I'm so happy to be with you.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Me too, Luna. I'm very happy right now.
